==German==

===Etymology===

From ''[[Eierschale]]'' ("egg shell"), ''[[Sollbruchstelle]]'' ("predetermined breaking point"), ''[[Verursacher]]'' ("causer").

===Noun===
'''Eierschalensollbruchstellenverursacher''' {{m}}

# ''A device used to create breaking points in egg shells in order to allow one to easily remove the top part of an egg using a knife without causing the shell to splinter.''

